          "innovator": "William Gilbert",
          "impact": "Distinguished 'electric' effects from magnetic ones; birth of the study of electricity."
        },
        {
          "year": "1745",
          "event": "Invention of the Leyden Jar",
          "innovator": "Ewald Georg von Kleist",
